# Phase 10 — Configure Environment Variables

Create:

```text
.env.local
```

Add:

```env
NEXT_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_URL=YOUR_PROJECT_URL
NEXT_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY=YOUR_ANON_KEY
```

Never commit this file.

